This repository contains a dataset and code created as part of the Open Data Armenia initiative.

The dataset was generated by extracting publicly available bibliographic metadata from the website of the Gomidas Institute:
https://www.gomidas.org

All copyrights, trademarks, and intellectual property rights for the original publications and materials belong to their respective owners, including the Gomidas Institute and the authors of the listed works.

This repository does not claim ownership of any original publications, texts, images, or other copyrighted materials referenced in the dataset. 
The dataset contains only structured metadata such as titles, authors, publication dates, descriptions, and links to the original sources.

The dataset was created to support open data, research, and digital humanities projects related to Armenian studies.

Users of this repository should ensure that any reuse of the data complies with applicable copyright laws and the terms of the original website.

The maintainers of this repository do not guarantee the completeness or accuracy of the dataset.
